src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDjSxWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDjSxWr.png&h=33e37f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家幫拖呀retweet呀<br />\n<br />\n全世界記得落<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">#PrayForJimmy</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ad12fcf3743b331394a2462e66cac0d4ba7b432","tid":1658483,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾時裝修我多數都支持你地！<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1017支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1018支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1019支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1020我屌你老母, 難得食個勢搞百萬行, 見返818個感覺返曬嚟, 一大班5毛就出嚟帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1021支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n..............</blockquote><br />\n星期日大遊行改做裝修？不了！我話你聽點解。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658541</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好嬲？聽日要見到文宣砌成o既10.20, 你先對得住岑子杰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">同埋保持憤怒, 今個星期是文宣週 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期日是和理非主場, 過埋星期日反佢枱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7oHaWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7oHaWT.jpg&h=75f2ea83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8be